Panzer::

Muttering under her breath,"scrap!" She transformed into bot mode and 
drew herside arm.  She stood up and took aim. Her sights moving from 
one to the other. "I'd recommend you stop right there. I don't want 
to have to shoot you."
Actually, she wanted to shoot them just because they were preds. But 
her maximal programming wouldn't allow her to shoot without a 
provoced attack. With the boulder shielding only 1/3rd of her body, 
she kept her ground.
